documentation.text:
@author Publius
 @title Gas efficient Constant Product pricing function for Wells with 2 tokens.
 Constant Product Wells with 2 tokens use the formula:
  `b_0 * b_1 = s^2`
 Where:
  `s` is the supply of LP tokens
  `b_i` is the reserve at index `i`
